FBIS4-63701 "drsov100_b_94001" FBIS-SOV-94-100 Daily Report 24 May 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political Issues Yeltsin Appoints Rybkin to Security Council Yeltsin Appoints Rybkin to Security Council LD2405065794 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 0652 GMT 24 May 94 LD2405065794 Moscow ITAR-TASS English BFN [Text] Moscow May 24 TASS -- Speaker of the Russian Parliament lower house Ivan Rybkin was appointed member of the Russian Security Council by a decree of President Boris Yeltsin, ITAR-TASS learnt at the presidential press service on Tuesday. This was done in connection with the signing of the Social Accord Treaty and in compliance with Article 83 of the Russian Constitution.
